g.text: A --> Marked, but internally disputed (e.g. claimed by other provinces)
B --> Disputed (claimed or controlled by other states)
(if C and D is used: claimed and de-facto controlled by other states
C --> Disputed (claimed by others while de-facto not controlled by others)
Use D&C with care. In most cases B&E and is sufficient.
Version: Beta 0.1. Note: v. 1.0 coming soon. Please "watch" the file.
